title: you ARE the main character! how to love yourself

description:
The gals are celebrating GALentines with an episode all about self love.  Brooke and Danielle share tips and ways they have learned to better their relationship with themselves.  The gals also share how to handle Valentine’s Day when you are single, and what their favorite self care tactics are!
